        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Iranian Military and Terror Financing Reporting Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of State to report to Congress annually on Iranian expenditures supporting foreign military and terrorist activities outside Iran.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
